getBounds in class MultipleThreadsPartition
Returns:
a shape containing all pair or thread segments of the partition. Adjacent hulls should not overlap but preferably touch one another with a (complex) line in stead of individual points.

getSwitchAt

public MultipleThreadsPartition getSwitchAt(int x,
                                            int y)
Searches for a Cross or Twist with the coordinates within its bounds. Zooms in on diagram sections as long as the specified position is within the bounds of the section.

Parameters:
x - position along the x-axis, zero is left, minus is out of sight
y - position along the y-axis, zero is top, minus is out of sight
Returns:
null or a Cross or Twist with the coordinates within its bounds.
